item.title: I wasn't allowed to be a Victim Shelby Jo Long
item.description: In this podcast episode featuring guest Shelby Jo Long, the conversation covers a wide range of topics, starting with the importance of effective communication skills, particularly in public speaking and business contexts. Travis and Shelby delve into entrepreneurship and various business ventures, including creating a communication-focused business and running a sports academy... item.title: Philippians 3:12-14
item.description: In this passage, Paul explains why he is content but not complacent. Paul sometimes compared the rigors of athletic training to Christian growth and development challenges. He believed Christians should never become complacent with where they were in their spiritual development. Growth is the natural desire of the mature Christian. Feed: https://podpoint.com/feed/5637
